Get started learning the basics of building great desktop apps in this section.

When you want to create a new desktop app, the first decision you make is whether to use the Win32 and COM API or .NET. C++ and Win32 gets you "closer to the metal," and lets you achieve the best performance for your app. .NET gets you to a higher level of coding and productivity with a less complex language. Learn which technology is best for your needs: [Choose Your Technology](https://msdn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/library/windows/desktop/dn614993.aspx).
